<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Monitoring - EduBridge</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }
        .container {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        h2 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 40px;
            font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;
        }
        .features {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .feature-item {
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .button {
            display: block;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #45a049;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    {{!-- {{> navbar}} <!-- Include the navigation bar --> --}}

    <div class="container">
        <h2>Monitor Your Progress and Opportunities</h2>
        
        <div class="features">
            <div class="feature-item">
                <h3>Industry Integrating Learning Outcomes</h3>
                <p>Explore specializations such as software development, engineering, and data science. Identify the skills employers seek and discover learning pathways to bridge your skills gap.</p>
                <button class="button" onclick="alert('Redirecting to learning pathways...')">View Learning Pathways</button>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-item">
                <h3>Timely Job and Internship Requirements</h3>
                <p>Stay updated with the latest job and internship announcements tailored for you. Get insights into the competencies required for each position.</p>
                <button class="button" onclick="alert('Fetching job and internship listings...')">View Job Listings</button>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-item">
                <h3>Mentoring and Webinars</h3>
                <p>Enhance your skills through webinars and mentoring programs conducted by industry specialists. Learn practical skills directly from the experts.</p>
                <button class="button" onclick="alert('Accessing mentoring programs...')">Join Mentoring Programs</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    {{> footer}} <!-- Include the footer -->

    <script>
        // Any additional JavaScript can go here
    </script>
</body>
</html>
